[Ceara is one of the 27 states of Brazil, located in the northeastern part of the country, on the Atlantic coast. It is the 8th-largest Brazilian State by population and the 17th by area. It is also one of the main tourist destinations in Brazil. The state capital is the city of Fortaleza, the country's 4th most populous city. - Mod.CP

