[This account provides some additional information, but it is unlikely that it will be established whether the event was a deliberate act or an accident.

Idlib governorate, which is the site of this incident, is held by moderate rebel groups opposed to both Syria's dictator, Bashar al-Assad, and the extremist Islamic State in Iraq and Syria (ISIS), according to the UNICEF report. - Mod.CP

